2026-05-04T00:59:22.6117935Z             "body": "## Summary\nAdded a clear button (×) to the domain input field that allows users to quickly reset the search input and view all available domain suggestions.\n\n## Key Changes\n- **UI Updates**: Added a new clear button positioned to the left of the dropdown arrow in the domain combo box\n  - Increased input right padding from `2.2rem` to `3.8rem` to accommodate the new button\n  - Clear button is hidden by default and only displayed when the input has a value\n  - Styled with hover effects matching the existing design system\n\n- **JavaScript Functionality**: Implemented clear button behavior\n  - Added `updateClearBtn()` function to toggle the `has-value` class based on input content\n  - Clear button clears the input value and reopens the suggestions dropdown\n  - Uses `mousedown` event to prevent input blur while maintaining focus\n  - Integrated `updateClearBtn()` calls into existing input handlers (selection, keystroke)\n\n## Implementation Details\n- The clear button uses the `×` character for a familiar UX pattern\n- Includes proper accessibility attributes (`title` and `aria-label`)\n- The button state is synchronized with input changes through the `has-value` CSS class\n- Maintains existing keyboard navigation and dropdown behavior\n\nhttps://claude.ai/code/session_017FwhhWhVeVAy86df4xWeVQ",
